To use QuickTime Pro  on Mac OS 10.6 you have to install QuickTime 7 Player from http://support.apple.com/kb/DL923 or original disk in addition to QuickTime X preinstalled, than follow http://support.apple.com/kb/HT3678 to activate Pro features and enjoy!
